      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDNITE MUSCLE (8) came from this barrier to continue his strong form and score at the most recent appearance at Bendigo, getting home by almost 2 metres. That gave him three wins and two placings from the last five starts. Can travel in a nice spot from this draw and the sprint lane is in play so has strong claims again. NIGHT FLIGHT (4) put the writing on the wall with back-to-back placings before he led for a last-start win by 11 metres at Ballarat. Draws a couple of spots wider but he is going well. GOLDEN SKIES (9) may need some luck from the back line but is going well, clocking in fourth at Melton last time to follow a Ballarat win. KENNYWOULD (10) won the only time he raced here and is going well enough to score again if things go his way from the back row.",
